metadata.name: Rumiñahui Volcano
metadata.description:
This is a panoramic view of the Rumiñahui Volcano. The volcano is part of the "Avenue of the Volcanos" in the ecuadorian Andes. This Avenue includes an approximate of 23 volcanos, from Inactive to currently intense activity. 
From the spot that I shot this image you can view the Sincholagua, Cotopaxi, Rumiñahui, Ilinizas and Pasochoa volcanos.
